            <div class="wrapper">  <div class="region region-featured">
    <div data-quickedit-entity-id="block_content/20" id="block-bandeauaccueil" class="contextual-region block-bandeauaccueil block block-block-content">
      
        <div data-contextual-id="block:block=bandeauaccueil:langcode=en|block_content:block_content=20:changed=1455895437&amp;langcode=en"></div>
        <div data-quickedit-field-id="block_content/20/body/en/full" class="field field-block-content--body field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden">
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item"><div class="img"><img alt="bandeau" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="b345446d-4445-4b99-9601-1f885d83ea15" height="250" src="/sites/default/files/inline-images/Bandeauweb-Nunavik_0.jpg" width="250" /></div>
<h2 class="date">Detention conditions, administration of justice<br />
and crime prevention in Nunavik</h2>
<p>In a report released on February 18, the Québec Ombudsman concluded that <strong>detention conditions in Nunavik are unacceptable</strong> and that crime prevention measure are woefully lacking.</p>
<p>This finding stemmed from a sweeping investigation conducted in villages in Nunavik, a territory of Quebec located north of the 55th parallel.</p>
<ul><li><a href="https://protecteurducitoyen.qc.ca/en/investigations-and-recommendations/special-reports/detention-conditions-Nunavik" title="Read more">Read more</a></li>
</ul></div>
      </div>
</div>

  </div>

  </div>
</div>
          </div>
        
                  <div class="home-situations wrapper">
              <div class="region region-home-situations">
      
      <h2>Common complaints</h2>
    <div data-contextual-id="block:block=situations:langcode=en|block_content:block_content=15:changed=1454526892&amp;langcode=en"></div>
  <div data-quickedit-field-id="block_content/15/field_header/en/full" class="field field-block-content--field-header field-name-field-header field-type-text-long field-label-above">
      <div class="field-label">Header</div>
    <div class="field-items">
          <div class="field-item"><p><a class="button" href="/en/make-a-complaint/how-to-make-a-complaint">How to make a complaint</a></p>
</div>
      </div>
</div>
<div class="situations">
      <div class="situation">
      <p class="icon-personnel">"I feel that the employee who handled my application was disrespectful."<br />
 </p>
<p><a class="button" href="https://protecteurducitoyen.qc.ca/en/search/node?keys=Staff+attitude+%22Staff+shortages+or+negligence%22&amp;f%5B0%5D=language%3Aenhttps://protecteurducitoyen.qc.ca/en/search/node?keys=%22Staff+shortages+or+negligence%22&amp;f%5B0%5D=language%3Aen">Other examples of staff attitude</a></p>

    </div>
      <div class="situation">
      <p class="icon-clock">"I can’t seem to be able to have my health insurance card renewed."<br />
 </p>
<p><a class="button" href="https://protecteurducitoyen.qc.ca/en/search/node?keys=%22Lengthy+wait+times%22&amp;f%5B0%5D=type%3Aresultats&amp;f%5B1%5D=language%3Aen">Other examples of wait times</a></p>

    </div>
      <div class="situation">
      <p class="icon-security">"I’m not getting all the home support hours I should have."<br />
 </p>
<p><a class="button" href="https://protecteurducitoyen.qc.ca/en/search/node?keys=%22Quality+of+care+and+services%22&amp;f%5B0%5D=type%3Aresultats&amp;f%5B1%5D=language%3Aen">Other examples of inaccessible services</a></p>

    </div>
      <div class="situation">
      <p class="icon-admin">''I received a notice of non-payment by mistake.''<br />
 </p>
<p><a class="button" href="https://protecteurducitoyen.qc.ca/en/search/node?keys=%22Administrative+inflexibility/errors%22&amp;f%5B0%5D=language%3Aenhttps://protecteurducitoyen.qc.ca/en/search/node?keys=%22Administrative+inflexibility/errors%22&amp;f%5B0%5D=type%3Aresultats&amp;f%5B1%5D=language%3Aen">Other examples of administrative errors</a></p>

    </div>
      <div class="situation">
      <p class="icon-incomplete">"I received a hospital room bill that I wasn’t informed about while I was hospitalized."<br />
 </p>
<p><a class="button" href="https://protecteurducitoyen.qc.ca/en/search/node?keys=%22Financial+damage%22&amp;f%5B0%5D=type%3Aresultats&amp;f%5B1%5D=language%3Aen">Other examples of incomplete information</a></p>

    </div>
  
  <div class="situation">
